; ShockRing: a thick-bordered hollow disk that scales out from the
; banner's center. Built as a ColorRect with rounded corners using
; corner_radius — at scale 0.1 it's a tiny dot, at scale 4 it's a
; ring large enough to overlap the playfield edges. Used to telegraph
; "something big just happened" the moment a banner pops.
