; Sparkles: CPUParticles2D one-shot burst tinted with the preset's color.
; Emits radially outward; gravity pulls them down slightly so they trail
; rather than float forever. The amount + spread combine to read as a
; "POW" of confetti at the banner's center.
[node name="Sparkles" type="CPUParticles2D" parent="."]
